data.description: GREAT VIEWS in BOYNTON BEACH! Waterfront, corner, first floor unit with amazing sunrises, Intracoastal+ views. Walk out of your patio to the pool, fitness center or to watch the Christmas Boat Parade or the 4th of July, or everyday life on the Intracoastal. This lovely 1200sf, 2 bedroom/2 bath has lots of closet space and is just begging for your touch of Florida style! Ventless W/D allowed. A/C 2018 W/H 2019, new GE Elec. Panel. Unit is offered turnkey. This is an active resort-style 55+ community with a waterfront, heated salt water pool and fitness center. Be minutes from trendy Atlantic Ave in Delray, beaches, restaurants, shopping and airports. Hurry to grab your piece of S. Florida living.
